Fabulous photo!  I thought it looked familiar,  like a Henry King photo.  Sure enough it is almost exactly the same position but at a different time.  The tree in the foreground is almost the same, so not too distant a date.  c.1895.
Then the photographer's name has been scratched out - I wonder if this was originally a King photo?  See - 

[http://www.flickr.com/photos/powerhouse_museum/2362707187/]
